comments:
Nicolas is a very friendly host who came to help me carrying my luggages ! 
His wife and his dog are adorable. The apt was clean.
I will definitely book this apartment again if I need a place to sleep in NYC;

- Beautiful place to stay;
- Quiet Neighborhood , far the from the crowd but near everything in NYC;
- Very clean and spacious ;
- Cozy place for families and friends;
- Would be here again for several times;
- CVS and supermarket very near;
- Helpful hosts;

Resume: 
PERFECT PLACE TO STAY !
